  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA generic centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (fully accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package represents a fully assessed, clean negative-control UnitOfAssurance in which all 13 credibility factors are assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel, provenance is complete, uncertainty quantification is documented, and the decision is Accepted. No weakener should fire on this package.",
